dct_title_s: Travel map of Taiwan : Northern Taiwan / Tourism Bureau. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Ancillary map on recto: Taipei City. Scale 1:24,800 -- Taipei MRT Routes. Map shows six classes of roads; railroads; national parks, scenic, and forest areas; tourist information. "Jan. 2011 printed." On cover: "TAIPEI INTL FLORA EXPO 2010/11/06-2011/04/25". On verso: Yangmingshan National Park -- North coast and Guanyinshan national scenic area -- Northeast and Yilan coast national scenic area -- Tri-mountain national scenic area -- Lion's Head Mountain -- Taipingshan National Forest recreation area.
